    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《完蛋！我被美女包围了！2》—— 古装奇缘，爱恨交织，你的选择决定一切！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小有内容工作室倾力打造的《完蛋！我被美女包围了！》系列正统续作，重磅回归！这一次，我们将带你步入波谲云诡的古代江湖与庙堂，体验一场前所未有的沉浸式恋爱互动冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经典阵容，惊喜重逢！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 为完美延续“完蛋宇宙”的魅力，我们力邀深受用户喜爱的原班人马华丽归来！无论是第一部中令人心动的郑梓妍、DLC里的夏天，还是前传中的元柒，她们都将以全新的古装扮相，在命运的牵引下与你再续前缘。准备好再次被她们独特的魅力征服了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/8d79fc4d37d83816e52d0fda84a49c05.poster.avif?t=1761011249\" width=612 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/8d79fc4d37d83816e52d0fda84a49c05.webm?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/8d79fc4d37d83816e52d0fda84a49c05.mp4?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>影视质感，全面升级！</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了实现影视化制作上的质感突破，我们与拥有深厚影视行业经验的<strong>欢瑞世纪</strong>强强联手，共同出品。顶尖的服化道设计、电影级的运镜与光影、专业制作班底的细心打磨，共同打造出远超同期作品的视听盛宴，为你带来堪比古装大片的沉浸式体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/8f458355cdee18ec42d44122e745840a.poster.avif?t=1761011249\" width=612 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/8f458355cdee18ec42d44122e745840a.webm?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/8f458355cdee18ec42d44122e745840a.mp4?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>心动不止，感动依旧！</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们深知，《完蛋》系列最打动人心的是那份真挚的情感共鸣、甜蜜的恋爱悸动和强烈的代入感。《完蛋！我被美女包围了！2》将<strong>完美继承这一核心</strong>，让你再次深陷与6位性格迥异的美女间的情感漩涡，体验心动、纠结、甜蜜与感动的每一刻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/a4665291e3f3653610dbbaea9cfdf728.poster.avif?t=1761011249\" width=612 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/a4665291e3f3653610dbbaea9cfdf728.webm?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/a4665291e3f3653610dbbaea9cfdf728.mp4?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>古装新篇，惊喜加码！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 不止于延续，更要大胆创新！《完蛋2》将舞台搬至古代，在唯美的古风背景下，融入了大量<strong>轻松诙谐的喜剧元素</strong>，让你在紧张冒险之余开怀一笑。除此之外，精心编织的<strong>权谋与悬疑主线</strong>正式登场！表面风花雪月，暗地却危机四伏，你身边的美女们，似乎也各自隐藏着不为人知的秘密...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/cb198ace4a36b1418c2fb049e4e39954.poster.avif?t=1761011249\" width=612 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/cb198ace4a36b1418c2fb049e4e39954.webm?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/cb198ace4a36b1418c2fb049e4e39954.mp4?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>双线并行，命运抉择！</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“情感线”与“悬疑线”双线交织的叙事结构。<strong>互动即人生，选择即代价！</strong> 没有人能全知全能：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ——若你<strong>随心而动，专注情缘</strong>，或许能不负美人恩，收获甜蜜结局，但也可能因沉溺温柔乡而错过揭示惊天阴谋的线索，最终对真相懵然不知。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ——若你<strong>执着真相，抽丝剥茧</strong>，反复探索每一个细节，或许能拨开迷雾，洞悉全局，但也可能因过于理智或深陷险境，最终与真心擦肩而过，落得孑然一身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/6da3fc1161b41ec5141ab9a44e8493e0.poster.avif?t=1761011249\" width=612 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/6da3fc1161b41ec5141ab9a44e8493e0.webm?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/6da3fc1161b41ec5141ab9a44e8493e0.mp4?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >孰是孰非？孰轻孰重？是“醉卧美人膝”还是“独醒探迷局”？没有标准答案，一切<strong>由你抉择</strong>！每一次选择都将导向截然不同的故事分支与结局，带来极高的重玩价值。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加量不加价，感动再出发！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 《完蛋！我被美女包围了！2》诚意满满，内容体量远超以往。我们再次以“一张电影票”的价格，诚挚邀请所有用户，<strong>重返2023年的那份初心与感动</strong>。准备好再一次心动了吗？这一次，在古色古香的江湖朝堂中，你的故事，等你亲自书写！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>角色介绍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >香闺蕙质·谢珂：心思缜密，肩负家族兴衰的谢家大小姐</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/572c08a12f272855483684c69b52a53f.poster.avif?t=1761011249\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/572c08a12f272855483684c69b52a53f.webm?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/572c08a12f272855483684c69b52a53f.mp4?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >碧玉玲珑·谢筱筱：天马行空，精力旺盛的谢家二小姐</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/6451d626237c24b011e6c3819792c617.poster.avif?t=1761011249\" width=612 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/6451d626237c24b011e6c3819792c617.webm?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/6451d626237c24b011e6c3819792c617.mp4?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寒刃孤影·阿宁：冷静老练，一切以任务为优先的神秘刺客</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/c0ef023a05ec911e53dcc764bacc605b.poster.avif?t=1761011249\" width=612 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/c0ef023a05ec911e53dcc764bacc605b.webm?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/c0ef023a05ec911e53dcc764bacc605b.mp4?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >花中魁首·柳施施：眼波流转间，似乎有一瞬停驻在你身上？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/f8da64d34cd85cfed9bb1a67d8cfa16f.poster.avif?t=1761011249\" width=612 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/f8da64d34cd85cfed9bb1a67d8cfa16f.webm?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/f8da64d34cd85cfed9bb1a67d8cfa16f.mp4?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蒙尘金枝·陆明月：生于宫廷，贯看朝堂风云变幻的长公主</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/fa482d536d22a943d91a36544e7f0ad1.poster.avif?t=1761011249\" width=612 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/fa482d536d22a943d91a36544e7f0ad1.webm?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/fa482d536d22a943d91a36544e7f0ad1.mp4?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >妙笔佳人·苏清儿：体弱多病，养在深闺的第一才女</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/7a8e49757a4b073e9d10913ce262d25b.poster.avif?t=1761011249\" width=612 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/7a8e49757a4b073e9d10913ce262d25b.webm?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282390/extras/7a8e49757a4b073e9d10913ce262d25b.mp4?t=1761011249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关注我们</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎关注我们了解《完蛋！我被美女包围了！》的最新进展：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B站：完蛋_我被美女包围了</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >微博：完蛋_我被美女包围了</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ①群：673376231（已满）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ②群：773989799（已满）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ③群：906084327（已满）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ④群：929476580（已满）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ⑤群：917082025<